      • ComboboxSearchOption

        public ComboboxSearchOption(String code,
                    String[] values,
                    String defaultValue,
                    String label)
        Default constructor.
        Parameters:
        code - Unique identifier for this option.
        values - List of values to display in the combo-box. The value of this options from Query.getExtendedOptionValue(String). will be one of these.
        defaultValue - The initially selected value in the combo-box. Must be one of values.
        label - An option label to display next to the combo-box or null if no label.

      • ComboboxSearchOption

        public ComboboxSearchOption(String code,
                    String[] values,
                    String defaultValue,
                    String label,
                    boolean editable)
        Parameters:
        code - Unique identifier for this option.
        values - List of values to display in the combo-box. The value of this options from Query.getExtendedOptionValue(String). will be one of these.
        defaultValue - The initially selected value in the combo-box. Must be one of values.
        label - An option label to display next to the combo-box or null if no label.
        editable - Whether or not the combo-box that represents this option should editable
